HEADWORD: Prelumbar
<hw>Pre*lum"bar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated immediately in front of the loins; -- applied to the
dorsal part of the abdomen.</def>⟦br⟧
